title: doc/code.html: Typo
body:
by **Lytvynov.A.V**: 
In the updated doc/code.html first example program's main is:
fmt.Printf("Hello, world.\n")

Later in compiled program's execution example we have:
$ $GOPATH/bin/hello
Hello!

And the same later:
$ hello
Hello!

Patch attached.
Attachments: 1. code.html.patch (315 bytes)
